yabel.code
Class CompilerOutput

java.lang.Object
  yabel.code.CompilerOutput

public class CompilerOutput
extends java.lang.Object

Intermediate output of the compilation system. Tracks labels and provides references for the code being generated.

Author:
Simon Greatrix
